#An ssh config file that will be mounted into
#nest_ops container at /ssh/config .
#This is needed to disable the prompt when connecting
#to the host for the first time that asks about
#the ssh id being unknown. This is the only way to
#disable it. (And there is no way to 'remember' it
#as there is not state in the nest_ops container.
Host *
	StrictHostKeyChecking  no


